description: Visually inspect each series connection between the control modules. Focus on ensuring that both of the cable pairs at each junction are attached properly, with no loose, disconnected, or partially inserted fast-connection terminals that might result in an open circuit. Look for signs of unseated connectors or poor mechanical fit., outcome='All control output and input cables (both (+) and (−)) at each junction have been visually inspected and are reported as properly connected, with no loose, disconnected, or unseated terminals. No observable internal faults or open circuit risks were detected in any cable. No polarity inversion was identified based solely on this inspection.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=280.0, cost_breakdown=[('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
